+Feature: Shipshape methodology
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Watchbill shape conforms when absent
+    Given the project root
+    When I check for a watchbill file
+    Then the watchbill conforms by absence
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: No perturbation token in implementation
+    Given the implementation directories
+    When I scan for the PERTURBATION token
+    Then no PERTURBATION token is found
